"{\"uid\": \"myrepublica.nagariknetwork.com-news-two-taiwanese-teenagers-win-world-robot-olympiad-in-india\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Subscribe Now  Whizzing around a green felt table chasing a soccer ball beaming infrared light, the boxy robot shoots and scores and wins its Taiwanese teenage creators first prize at this year's student robot games.The two breadbox-sized scooters, playing goalie and kicker, from the team called 'Wings of Storm' were up against another Taiwanese team's robots in the 'Football' category of the World Robot Olympiad held over the weekend in the Indian capital of New Delhi.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 338, \"end\": 347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.986729959625004, \"rank\": 0.010450186189792167, \"text\": \"Taiwanese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 396, \"end\": 416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Robot_Olympiad\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Robot Olympiad\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Robot_Olympiad\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Robot_Olympiad\"}, {\"begin\": 446, \"end\": 452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9683846070374479, \"rank\": 0.023054547086109028, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 464, \"end\": 473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"score\": 0.9999995327049146, \"rank\": 4.6729515570897654e-07, \"text\": \"New Delhi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have been practicing since primary school and are thrilled to have won.\